{"tid":1651821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出面打緊仗, 返到嚟又見到連登又同國難嘈...","createTime":"2019-10-13T12:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:33:24.000Z","uid":69291,"like":55,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9533a67bca31eaa665729f7a786bc308b6ebfdb2","tid":1651821,"uid":69291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"其實大家係唔係唔識咩叫冷處理？<br />\n係呀, 佢加價呀又唔開鋪呀<br />\n係呀, 佢做生意唔係一定要平賣畀你嫁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我想問嘈撚完未？<br />\n嘈唔撚完嫁屌你老母<br />\n今日都未完就嘈嘈嘈<br />\n尋日互屌仲未屌夠？<br />\n今日又拉咗百幾人喇最少<br />\n無國難係唔係唔可以上網買落嚟再自己拎畀前線？<br />\n係呀上網買好耐都未到呀<br />\n屌你今日唔買, 下世都唔會到呀<br />\n仲有<br />\n聽晚集會做好文宣叫咗人未？<br />\n下星期啲行動點？<br />\n又話一個星期做文宣？<br />\n係咪畀你屌贏就會支爆呀？<br />\n係咪畀你屌贏就唔會有手足失蹤唔會有手足死呀？<br />\n係呀, 我係好撚嬲呀<br />\n嬲你地成日互屌呀<br />\n佢唔賣, 唔開鋪你地第一時間係搵下有咩方法幫到前線補給呀<br />\n你地互屌緊既時候, 前線食緊棍食緊煙食緊子彈呀<br />\n醒下啦屌<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"60bb4451fdf86c2d84f789a9dca25b8bcd25e56b","tid":1651821,"uid":69291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F5jiOPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF5jiOPB.jpg&h=6934a2bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ajMhjWi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FajMhjWi.jpg&h=2b49a40a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bfda0c2f835c98b9d0e12e0443cdf3ae8fec499","tid":1651821,"uid":69291,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7mQEWw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7mQEWw.jpg&h=57c8d960&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11dc628fcd46200d277499bcef85a1b041b42e1f","tid":1651821,"uid":69291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:01:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">識唱美國國歌未呀？</span></span>"},{"pid":"da9